OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Body Shop's UK business has entered
OL,6, administration, potentially putting up 
OL,7, to 2,000 jobs at risk.                 
OL,9,FThe retailer's shops will remain open  
OL,10,Fas usual while efforts are made to try 
OL,11,Fto save the UK firm.                   
OL,13,FRestructuring firm FRP, which has been 
OL,14,Fappointed as the administrator, said it
OL,15,Fwould now consider all options to find 
OL,16,Fa way forward for the business.        
OL,18,FThe Body Shop was started by the late  
OL,19,FDame Anita Roddick in 1976 from a      
OL,20,Fsingle shop in Brighton.               
